{"tid":1478508,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔好養狗」美聯前線分行樓盤單張遭移除","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:06:22.000Z","uid":271105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8233c0e980f62a92d2b2ba73549b22bd696fece7","tid":1478508,"uid":271105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】「唔好養狗」樓盤宣傳單張遭移除 傳美聯高層警告前線分行<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190816&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59939120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190816%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59939120&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0axOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=cbaa04ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190816%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59939120&h=baf4d464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190816&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59939120</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjhLT39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjhLT39.jpg&h=f6ca73e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日市場流傳，美聯物業栢蕙苑分行有宣傳單張，改用黑色作底色，更用「<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好養狗</span></strong></span>」以及「<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非</span></strong></span>」等敏感字眼，並刻意加大「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span></strong></span>」字，但其後不久便移除相關宣傳單張。市場消息指，是由於<strong>涉及敏感字眼及政治取態</strong>，因此被管理層警告。<br />\n<br />\n美聯栢蕙苑區域經理練卓航指，警告主要是針對宣傳單張用色和格式與公司要求有出入，而並非針對單張所用的字眼。<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">至於宣傳單張上「唔好養狗」字眼，乃是放盤業主的真實要求，至於「<span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非</span>」則是解作「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和諧、理性、非離地價</span>」，並沒有其他隱含意思。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而美聯物業行政總裁布少明指，宣傳單張是前線分行同事察覺不妥後自行移除，但對事件將不會再多作評論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">地產佬connected<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[size=4]有朋友嘅朋友嘅屋企人係呢間栢蕙苑分行員工，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>聽朝準備俾膠層照肺</strong></span>，<strong>希望大家可以幫忙send email去HR嗰邊支持下佢地</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[/size=3]<br />\n雖然冇直線email，希望大家都花啲時間去填呢條link入面嘅form：<a href=\"https://app.midland.com.hk/email/sendEmail.jsp?langw=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.midland.com.hk%2Femail%2FsendEmail.jsp%3Flangw%3Dzh&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0axOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=77363015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app.midland.com.hk/email/sendEmail.jsp?langw=zh</a>"},{"pid":"78a8a25dfa1fed57ed859846931098f6e02eb7eb","tid":1478508,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74df8b8fc46458f5dc7356e44f175b8a2320470e","tid":1478508,"uid":171326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}